係車流, 太多車行既問題, 令公路飽和<br />\n十幾年前都無咁多塞車, 以前上廣洲夜晚少d 車, 可以一個鐘頭就到<br />\n而家多左路, 反而慢左, 最少要1.5-2hrs<br />\n<br />\n以前未有公路免費都長假期都會塞<br />\n原本以前普遍認為假期因為公路收費, 所以引至塞車<br />\n收錢收得慢<br />\n<br />\n所以後黎提倡免費通行, 希望快d 放車過橋, 上高速公路, 流通快d, 唔會塞<br />\n<br />\n唔好掉轉講 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e0034e60073b3a5f4204e802c4624af70bdca4d","tid":421430,"uid":16676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T09:32:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>長假期高鐵, 動車, 火車都唔一定買到飛, <br />\n買到亦唔會係即班<br />\n唔同地鐵, 通勤<br />\n去到車站可以即時過飛入閘, 即走<br />\n利申: 試過...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有次係天河買飛落深圳<br />\n已經買唔到即班, 即時走<br />\n然後又delay 左成一個鐘<br />\n最後計返由到廣州東計, 去到深圳用左4-5hrs, 明明無事無幹<br />\n唔係天氣問題 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n當初只係諗火車落深圳應該又快,又舒服 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dda4e5cd7198de537631c0d8aca8df55f47b7e16","tid":421430,"uid":16676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T09:35:20.000Z","msg":"以前就係長假期, 本來平日唔揸開車果班都揸車出黎<br />\n公路又收費, 所以攪到塞車<br />\n<br />\n就算公路收唔收錢, 亦會有假日司機 (無咭,無自動繳費, 唔知收幾錢, 無準備散銀)<br />\n所以最後不如唔收錢, 等佢地快d 過, 快d 走 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a5cff41051737b0bd016019c3e62c1350479b6d","tid":421430,"uid":49316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T09:59:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>今年特登搞到咁<br />\n為高鐵鋪路</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實年年都係咁，只係今年特別嚴重<br />\n死因係所有公路免費，你知班支那人咩都貪架啦</blockquote><br />\n張五常好似一早屌過呢樣野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n仲有成堆中國經濟學家我見都有屌，呢d中學econ<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n無計d領導人學位都係買返黎，或者考完試就算</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n班支那人好似F1 起步。十二點前係收費站前等<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d29d98514e7a58638e05952cfb569c5cf808934","tid":421430,"uid":121989,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T10:01:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>以前就係長假期, 本來平日唔揸開車果班都揸車出黎<br />\n公路又收費, 所以攪到塞車<br />\n<br />\n就算公路收唔收錢, 亦會有假日司機 (無咭,無自動繳費, 唔知收幾錢, 無準備散銀)<br />\n所以最後不如唔收錢, 等佢地快d 過, 快d 走 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n長假highway 唔收錢"},{"pid":"1d766c84c13ef4247739bac665543fd6a0941594","tid":421430,"uid":37463,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T10:04:09.000Z","msg":"屌 , 係要返鄉下 , 你高速收幾貴都會俾架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n關收唔收錢咩事<br />\n收錢仲有機會 司機唔夠錢/到左先搵銀包/入錯auto .....<br />\n全免費理論上係會快左<br />\n但支那d路咁濕鳩， 地下無線任人cut , 加到10 條線一邊都係會塞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n這就是支那<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c0025b5ae8713ef82b74e74bf02f9491a576c3c","tid":421430,"uid":66759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T10:15:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5586b74bfd586a3bce866be5d065c55d2195461d","tid":421430,"uid":136994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T10:23:44.000Z","msg":"中國人<br />\n一起共享大塞車的榮耀吧！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5ad26f9476223b9872c4fdbf693b2c6b61c1c4f","tid":421430,"uid":49643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T10:26:06.000Z","msg":"一向都係咁，但係今年咁岩香港撞正星期六日，連放幾日假，先會影響埋直通巴士"},{"pid":"9d902842f99121a88fdfbd2d59a9a9898b9d7f7d","tid":421430,"uid":62599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T10:32:08.000Z","msg":"都係虎門塞爆<img src=\"/assets/fac